Varela Romero, J R
Gallego Carracedo, E
metadata.dc:description: We present three cases of double pylorus, one of them of iatrogenic origin, the latter entity being extremely rare. Likewise we review the etiopathogenic theories.
metadata.dc:title: Doble canal pilórico. Presentación de tres nuevos casos y revisión de la literatura.
[Double pyloric canal. Presentation of 3 new cases and review of the literature].
metadata.dc:publisher: Revista espanola de las enfermedades del aparato digestivo
